Thai. is one ot the reasons why wars are so careful.
It is interesting that the critics of the Vietnam war tend to
criticism it because war is dreadful, but [hell they tend to criticism
that which goes to make war dreadlul. it it were possible to wage
wars without killing people, or destroyingeiarms, houses, afterwards, and schools, then was‘ worlds't be dreadful. is it low much
to ask that they at least accept the ontological structure of war,
